{"tid":1497843,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"已fc！！tg傾大事必須要用太空卡","createTime":"2019-08-23T06:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T02:20:46.000Z","uid":219269,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0cb3fc38a812ed5fd1e728f971961d725f6690f8","tid":1497843,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:57:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家認真啲得唔得，樓主其實講得冇錯，我昨天都做咗個實驗，發現telegram喺香港真係好危險！！！！<br />\n首先我加1萬個電話入我部android contact list, 我揀咗6018 0000至 6018 9999<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q19n3N6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ19n3N6.jpg&h=6841a066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後入telegram contact list 睇，真係add到堆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jPkyq2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjPkyq2d.jpg&h=939cdad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我是但揀啲group睇下裡，驚嚇嘅事件發生了，個電話顯示出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fWbmzWi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfWbmzWi.jpg&h=328deab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nSJDCax.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnSJDCax.jpg&h=5b5da353&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n最驚嘅係，我可以睇你講過咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LAvB8hy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLAvB8hy.jpg&h=343a75db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n試想像，有國家級力量，重複我以上動作，根本好易，用真電話玩telegram自己睇路</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三千萬個電話號碼真係唔算得係咩<br />\n保障自己好緊要"},{"pid":"884912ad2dec6bbd3e10b03409334073373be1d2","tid":1497843,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:58:02.000Z","msg":"［警告］Telegram會暴露個人電話號碼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ktffgyX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ktffgyX</a><br />\n#206 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4e2ae299f2c7c347b1581754115f42eb4943a927","tid":1497843,"uid":61084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:21:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對抗邪惡係唔可以心存僥倖</span></span>"},{"pid":"f450bb9a64e03daf4480f4edf56ddfae75f76985","tid":1497843,"uid":53411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:24:15.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">所以一定要太空卡\n唔好用自己電話[sosad]</code></pre>"},{"pid":"65a69a352a48607a4c93b2d1c9a33aa7f6b2b117","tid":1497843,"uid":35382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:25:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"03a12fa92e847f611001bf4981b9ab38c821f7d8","tid":1497843,"uid":241869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:35:28.000Z","msg":"其實可以邪惡d諗，電訊商俾左電話號碼國家機器試<br />\n咁咪仆街"},{"pid":"060f417d7df7f133417c9981f9e7aa3092a61a1a","tid":1497843,"uid":19337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:20:46.000Z","msg":"1. 呢個係 telegram group 設計問題，我覺得係一個漏洞<br />\n2. 八個位既香港電話可以 brute force add 晒的話，美國號碼要試晒的話，都應該技術上可行？ <br />\n3. 係咪要考慮放棄 telegram ?"}]}